high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the plate up from the counter.
Go to the right and face the sink.
Put the plate in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the plate up again.
Move to the left and stand next to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the plate down on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on the counter.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the kitchen counter to the left of the sink
grab the dirty plate off of the kitchen counter there
move to the right a bit and face the kitchen sink
place the plate inside the sink and clean it off
move left a bit towards the left side of the kitchen counter to the left of the stove, but then turn right and face away from the counter top
place the plate down on the kitchen counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a clean plate down on the kitchen counter to the right of the sink

high_descs: Turn around and head to the counter to the left of the sink
Pick up the dirty plate that is sitting on the counter to the right of the pan
Take a step to the right and stand in front of the sink
Place the plate in the sink and turn on the faucet to rinse off the plate, then turn off the faucet and pick up the clean plate
Take a step over to your left to stand in front of the counter to the left of the sink, then turn right to face the counter to the right of the sink
Place the clean plate on the counter to the right of the sink by the egg
anns.task_desc: Place a clean plate on a counter
